snippet.title: Dream Card tease trailer ft. selected NFT cards
snippet.description: Dream Card are digital, collectible characters built on the Ethereum blockchain and Binance Smart Chain. They can be bought and sold using XWG token, and bred to create new characters with exciting traits and varying levels of cuteness, powerful cards to battle and trade.
